<div class="title">As a Sleep Aid</div>
<div class="substance">Diazepam (Valium)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Shadowman&Exact=1">Shadowman</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Shadowman. "As a Sleep Aid: An Experience with Diazepam (Valium) (exp80417)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 6, 2009. erowid.org/exp/80417</div>

<br/>



